An environment with the following config should just generate a CSS output running `patternplate-console build-bundles`:

``` json
{
    "name": "only-css",
    "displayName": "Only CSS",
    "display": true,
    "version": "0.1.0",
    "include": ["*/**"],
    "formats": ["css"],
    "environment": {
        "transforms": {}
    }
}
```

Running this will throw the error:

```
